{"tid":2495214,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"環時：台灣買通全日本媒體，大幅報導日美聯合聲明提及台灣","createTime":"2021-04-19T05:07:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T06:13:58.000Z","uid":337052,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"64eba42f3af0408ecdb2f7134ad040780ff611e5","tid":2495214,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T05:07:04.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">&ldquo;台灣&rdquo;包下日媒各大報頭版後，島內網友嗅出了陰謀和危險</span></strong><br />\n來源：<span class=\"red\">環球網</span>作者：尹艷輝<br />\n<br />\n2021-04-19 11:02<br />\n<br />\n【環球網報導】<span class=\"red\">日本學者小笠原欣幸18日在臉書發出貼文，稱日本報紙頭條都是&ldquo;台灣&rdquo;，不只頭版，內頁的大篇幅報導也都圍繞台灣。</span>他還在貼文中附上一張日本4份報紙頭版照片，<span class=\"red\">包括《讀賣新聞》《產經新聞》《朝日新聞》及《每日新聞》，都以頭版頭條報導&ldquo;日美聯合聲明提及台灣&rdquo;</span>。<br />\n<br />\n日本首相菅義偉與美國總統拜登於北京時間17日凌晨在白宮舉行會談，兩人在會後聯合聲明中對台海局勢表達&ldquo;關切&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n在這兩人會談之前，就有一些人渲染他們的聯合聲明將提&ldquo;台海&rdquo;。中國外交部發言人趙立堅4月16日在記者會上表示，&ldquo;日美應該嚴肅對待中方關切和要求，不得採取干涉中國內政，損害中國利益的言行，不得搞針對中國的小圈子。<span class=\"red\">中方將視情作出必要回應</span>。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n小笠原欣幸18日的臉書貼文，迅速引發島內關注，&ldquo;中央社&rdquo;引述小笠原欣幸的說法，稱&ldquo;沒看過台灣佔這麼大的版面&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://rs1.huanqiucdn.cn/dp/api/files/imageDir/19e5bff717082d68a1fc02f134b97510u1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs1.huanqiucdn.cn%2Fdp%2Fapi%2Ffiles%2FimageDir%2F19e5bff717082d68a1fc02f134b97510u1.png&h=3f5c9a86&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"44d48cdf7fdca291006d2ff5d93247702bc49ded","tid":2495214,"uid":217641,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T05:08:09.000Z","msg":"成個共產黨摺柒左佢咪有頭版囉"},{"pid":"abf4e442e368e7afe3ab9faa956478f3741bea4b","tid":2495214,"uid":337052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T05:08:57.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">台灣占據日本報紙頭條 日學者：從沒看過</span></strong><br />\n最新更新：2021/04/18 13:16<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgcdn.cna.com.tw/www/WebPhotos/1024/20210418/2000x1500_0254942461922.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgcdn.cna.com.tw%2Fwww%2FWebPhotos%2F1024%2F20210418%2F2000x1500_0254942461922.jpg&h=8eca6cb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本學者小笠原欣幸18日在臉書貼文指出日本報紙頭條都是「台灣」，顯現日美聯合聲明包含台灣的重要性。（<a href=\"http://圖取自facebook.com/ogasawara.yoshiyuki\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%9C%96%E5%8F%96%E8%87%AAfacebook.com%2Fogasawara.yoshiyuki&d=CDYmK9DOGPUFxvwNhHfqx3GrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=92bf1c63\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">圖取自facebook.com/ogasawara.yoshiyuki</a>）<br />\n<br />\n（中央社台北18日電）日本學者小笠原欣幸今天在臉書貼文說，<span class=\"red\">日本報紙頭條都是「台灣」，不只頭版，內頁也大篇幅報導，都圍繞台灣，「我個人沒看過台灣占這麼大的版面」，顯現日美聯合聲明包含台灣的重要性。</span><br />\n<br />\n小笠原貼文中附上一張日本4份報紙頭版照片，包括讀賣新聞、產經新聞、朝日新聞及每日新聞，都以頭版頭條報導日美聯合聲明提及台灣。<br />\n<br />\n日本首相菅義偉15日率團訪美，台灣時間17日凌晨跟美國總統拜登進行日美領袖會談，全程歷時約兩個半小時；這次會談是雙方首度面對面會談，會後發表聯合聲明。<br />\n<br />\n有關中國定位為「核心利益」的台灣，聯合聲明載明，在強調台灣海峽和平與安定重要性同時，推動和平解決兩岸問題。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">這是繼1969年時任日本首相佐藤榮作與美國總統尼克森會面以來，日美再度在領袖會談聯合聲明中載明台灣，同時也是從1972年日本與中國建交以來的首度。</span>（編輯：黃名璽、蔡佳敏）1100418<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202104180073.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffirstnews%2F202104180073.aspx&d=CDYmK9DOGPUFxvwNhHfqx3GrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=ddb2a8b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202104180073.aspx</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/EUEa580aoOsmNGLFHqBLqg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTkyNS41ODQ5MDU2NjAzNzczO2NmPXdlYnA-/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/0FhUsisFCH9dSHCweA5LNA--~B/aD01MTE7dz01MzA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/nownews.com/d2f7298d5ed19580e2c6a6b852114b83\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FEUEa580aoOsmNGLFHqBLqg--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTkyNS41ODQ5MDU2NjAzNzczO2NmPXdlYnA-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F0FhUsisFCH9dSHCweA5LNA--~B%2FaD01MTE7dz01MzA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fnownews.com%2Fd2f7298d5ed19580e2c6a6b852114b83&h=40ef9a6f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"04ed277d205078099f7f84fd32440fb86e5ce2eb","tid":2495214,"uid":337052,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T05:10:31.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">台灣買通全日本媒體</span><br />\n這要花多少錢？中共以為民主國家的媒體都可以用錢買！"},{"pid":"d5f1e1091ece782909ced22c63ed8c2fcab58495","tid":2495214,"uid":41116,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T05:11:09.000Z","msg":"一時又笑人又窮又亂 一時又有錢到買起全日本傳媒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea9260e3694985d0f0b9389644678b87ed8941a7","tid":2495214,"uid":71237,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T05:12:04.000Z","msg":"你又買囉"},{"pid":"7b24f9ff7fd2765fa038101d04f0eb0f9e93b1b1","tid":2495214,"uid":337052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d5f1e1091ece782909ced22c63ed8c2fcab58495","tid":2495214,"uid":41116,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T05:11:09.000Z","msg":"一時又笑人又窮又亂 一時又有錢到買起全日本傳媒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T05:12:34.000Z","msg":"台灣的晶片都是靠中共賺錢的<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"647a106592068a4d73931704b30b1ba0a8925eff","tid":2495214,"uid":50386,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T05:12:47.000Z","msg":"支那全部傳媒都係黨媒<br />\n點會明白新聞自由係咩嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27b50ad8293725810ddf4d7e7b46f3eca2e470f7","tid":2495214,"uid":337119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T05:13:12.000Z","msg":"點都唔好俾支媒買通"},{"pid":"c872a298733321304513a1efad79d043db48b702","tid":2495214,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"647a106592068a4d73931704b30b1ba0a8925eff","tid":2495214,"uid":50386,"lik